14 TO REPEAL THE LAW CONCERNING THE REVIEW
15 OF INFORMATION TECHNOLOGY PLANS.
16
17 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF ARKANSAS:
18
19 SECTION 1. Arkansas Code ยง 19-11-269 is repealed.
20 19-11-269. Review of information technology plans.
21 The Office of State Procurement shall ensure that all required
22 information has been submitted to the Office of Intergovernmental Services
23 for review of proper planning and technical requirements before the execution
24 of:
25 (1) A contract issued under this subchapter that procures
26 information technology products or services with a total projected contract
27 amount, including any amendments to or possible extensions of the contract,
28 of at least one hundred thousand dollars ($100,000); or
29 (2) A purchase of information technology products or services
30 made under a cooperative purchase agreement under ยง 19-11-249.
